  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see if memantine is helpful in managing problematic symptoms
      in adults with autism, Asperger's disorder, or Pervasive Developmental Disorder not otherwise
      specified (NOS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
